      • serializeMapData

        public MapData serializeMapData(int gameType,
                                int index)
        Returns the MapData messenger class for the specified map index of the specified game mode
        Parameters:
        gameType - The game mode (freeplay, campaign etc.) that contains the requested map. Enumeration: 0 = Freeplay
        index - The index of the requested map. Determines which directory will be searched for the Map.xml file
        Returns:
        The MapData for the specified map

      • serializeAllGoalData

        public java.util.ArrayList<GoalData> serializeAllGoalData(int gameType,
                                                          int index)
        Returns the GoalData messenger classes for all of the goals for the specified map index of the specified game mode.
        Parameters:
        gameType - The game mode (freeplay, campaign etc.) that contains the requested map. Enumeration: 0 = Freeplay
        index - The index of the requested map. Determines which directory will be searched for the Goals.xml file
        Returns:
        An arraylist containing each of the map goals for the requested map, indexed by their corresponding faction

      • serializeAllUnitData

        public java.util.ArrayList<UnitData> serializeAllUnitData(int gameType,
                                                          int index)
        Returns the UnitData messenger classes for all of the units for the specified map index of the specified game mode.
        Parameters:
        gameType - The game mode (freeplay, campaign etc.) that contains the requested map. Enumeration: 0 = Freeplay
        index - The index of the requested map. Determines which directory will be searched for the Units.xml file
        Returns:
        An arraylist containing each of the map goals for the requested map, indexed by their in-game array indices
